Class Load_Activity

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.app.Activity
      • android.support.v4.app.FragmentActivity
        • android.support.v7.app.ActionBarActivity
          • com.example.bookshelf_initialpage.Load_Activity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ActionBarDrawerToggle.DelegateProvider, TaskStackBuilder.SupportParentable

    public class Load_Activity
extends ActionBarActivity
    LoadActivity renders a ListView with all the files from the SDcard of the AVD. When the user clicks on one item the item gets selected. Two buttons one to Load the item onto BookShelf and another to delete from Bookshelf enables to load and delete a book from the list onto and from the bookshelf respectively
    Author:
    Anjana Chatta
